title: Collection of books and articles--academic, fiction, non-fiction
description:
Large collection of over 5,000 books, book chapters, articles, and dissertations. Many are "academic" but there are also popular fiction and non-fiction works. All files should be searchable by either extracted or OCR text. This collection contains many works that can be found in other similar collections, but in those cases the files here have been meticulously processed, cropped, optimized, etc., to get the most readable and searchable document with the smallest file size. Most are in PDF format, and where possible original pagination has been retained for citation purposes.

Subjects are wide-ranging, including philosophy, religion, anthropology, queer theory, literature and literary criticism, gender studies, sexuality studies, and social theory
